OL,3,C'I'll stay until the war is over' -
OL,4,Caid worker living in his car in Ukraine
OL,6,FTwo West Country volunteers are
OL,7,Frisking their lives to help support
OL,8,Fpeople in war-torn Ukraine.
OL,10,FAndy Matheson, a builder from Beer in
OL,11,FDevon, travelled to Ukraine shortly
OL,12,Fafter the war started and has vowed
OL,13,Fnot to return until it is over.
OL,15,FHe has been helping villagers rebuild
OL,16,Ftheir homes as well as delivering much-
OL,17,Fneeded aid and medical supplies close
OL,18,Fto the front line.
