OL,3,C'I'll stay until the war is over' -
OL,4,Caid worker living in his car in Ukraine
OL,6,FIn one video, Andy described arriving
OL,7,Fat a village just after it had come
OL,8,Funder fire and had to take refuge
OL,9,Fwhile other shells fell. He said as a
OL,10,Fformer soldier, he was not afraid and
OL,11,Fknew the risks.
OL,13,FHe told ITV News West Country: "I'm an
OL,14,Fex-soldier, it doesn't bother me
OL,15,Fgreatly. I don't take any chances, if
OL,16,Fwe see it, we obviously take cover and
OL,17,Fjust wait for it too finish and then
OL,18,Fcarry on with whatever we are doing
OL,19,Fthat day."
