OL,3,C'I'll stay until the war is over' -
OL,4,Caid worker living in his car in Ukraine
OL,6,FAndy is living in his car while he is
OL,7,Fin Ukraine and is relying on
OL,8,Ffundraising through the and family and
OL,9,Ffriends to provide enough money to pay
OL,10,Ffor his fuel and the upkeep of his car.
OL,12,FHe said: "Family and friends and
OL,13,Fstrangers have been very, very kind,
OL,14,Fvery generous and kept me going with
OL,15,Fdonations... I just put out appeals on
OL,16,FFacebook and things and people come
OL,17,Fthrough time and again. Just when I
OL,18,Fthink, there's no more money, I'll go
OL,19,Fback home, people keep pumping money."
