OL,3,C'I'll stay until the war is over' -
OL,4,Caid worker living in his car in Ukraine
OL,6,FOne of those who've helped fundraise
OL,7,Fis Danny Potts from Torpoint. He met
OL,8,FAndy in Ukraine when he too went out
OL,9,Fto help. He plans to go back out to
OL,10,FUkraine next month for at least six
OL,11,Fmonths.
