OL,3,C'I'll stay until the war is over' -
OL,4,Caid worker living in his car in Ukraine
OL,6,FDanny has opened his home in Torpoint
OL,7,Fto Ukrainian Hanna Zoschuk, who has
OL,8,Farrived in the last few days from
OL,9,FOdessa. A singer and vocal coach, she
OL,10,Fis hoping to find work here but says
OL,11,Fthe situation in Ukraine is desperate.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's unfair what's happened
OL,14,Fand (people are) dying, dying,
OL,15,Fespecially kids. Thank you Danny, Andy
OL,16,Ffor supporting our kids especially."
